These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, woodworking, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, whist, scrabble
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Game   | snooker | chess | scrabble | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, coffee, almond-milk
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk | coffee | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, scrabble, domino
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
2. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
3. the person playing domino is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Game   | backgammon | monopoly | domino | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, 7up, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | 7up | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, parkour, handball
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
3. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Sport   | parkour | climbing | handball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cricket, weightlifting, volleyball
