2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Sport   | volleyball | tennis | weightlifting | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-8::.
City: london, hamburg, boston, nizza
1. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
| City   | boston | hamburg | nizza | london |

