.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, police-officer, manager, coach
1. the videographer is on the right of the coach##1
2. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1
3. the police-officer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Job   | manager | police-officer | coach | videographer |

