.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, soul, trance, blues
1. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
2. the fan of trance is between the fan of soul and the fan of house##2
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | trance | house | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, van, taxi, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
4. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Transport   | taxi | ship | boat | van |

