.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-17::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, turtle, rat
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |  3   |     4     |
| Pet   | bird | rat | turtle | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, december, august, january
1. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | january | july | august | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, board-games, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games | fishing | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, mouse, snake
1. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | snake | mouse | ferret |

 